‚öôÔ∏è Mini Shell Script Examples (Practice Tasks)
1.	Script to Check if a Service is Running
bash
CopyEdit
#!/bin/bash
if systemctl is-active --quiet nginx
then
  echo "Nginx is running"
else
  echo "Nginx is not running"
fi
2.	Cron Job Example (Run Script at 2 AM Daily)
bash
CopyEdit
0 2 * * * /home/user/backup.sh
3.	One-liner to Find Files Modified in Last 1 Day
bash
CopyEdit
find /var/log -type f -mtime -1
